@adelapena ok that took a while to pin down. There were concurrency issues with the sets keeping track of the indices, which lead to wrong `failedIndexes` lists triggering the NPE. The fix is [here](https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/dd0a598c8fa29b3bfcda1ec66c9190904a84b10d#diff-3f2c8994c4ff8748c3faf7e70958520dR489). It was a legit bug :-)

I did run the test 1K times and it passed. Now waiting on CI.

